          <p class="parrafo_2">1. National Collection of Plant Pathogenic Bacteria (NCPPB), Central Science Laboratory, York, Reino Unido.</p>
          <p class="parrafo">2. Culture Collection of the Plant Protection Service (PD), Wageningen, Países Bajos.</p>
          <p class="parrafo">3. Collection Française de Bactéries Phytopathogènes (CFBP) — INRA Station Phytobactériologie, Angers, Francia.</p>
